thread.title: Michael Fox

author: Michael Fox
title: Michael Fox
text: Worked very well to get competitive prices on rental and insurance. You do end up dealing directly with the original supplier (eg Avis) and if you have an insurance claim, you pay Avis, then claim back through the AirportRentals insurer, which I didn't realise until I picked up the car, but it never eventuated anyway. Overall everyting worked seemlessly and I am happy with the service
